Package com.codigofacilito.fastmatrix

Class MatrixUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codigofacilito.fastmatrix.MatrixUtils
  • public class MatrixUtils
extends java.lang.Object
    The MatrixUtils class provides a set of utility methods for manipulating matrices and vectors. These methods include printing matrices and vectors, extracting specific rows, columns, and diagonals, as well as creating matrices of zeros, ones, and identity matrices. Additionally, it includes methods for transposing matrices and editing specific rows or columns of matrices.
